<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Araba Marketim - Hoş Geldiniz</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body,
        html {
            height: 100%;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }

        .landing-page {
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-image: url('/images/bg1.png');
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            position: relative;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: left;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #e31837;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #c41230;
        }

        .button.secondary {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #ffffff;
        }

        .button.secondary:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="landing-page">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>ArabaMarketim'e Hoş Geldiniz</h1>
            <p>Türkiye'nin en kapsamlı araba markası ve model bilgi platformuna hoş geldiniz. Hesabınıza giriş yapın
                veya yeni bir hesap oluşturun.</p>
            <div class="buttons">
                <a href="/login" class="button" onclick="navigateTo('/login')">Giriş Yap</a>
                <a href="/register" class="button secondary" onclick="navigateTo('/register')">Kayıt Ol</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        function navigateTo(url) {
            window.location.href = url;
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>